dc_title_s: Kukaku kaisei Ōsaka no zu Katō Shūzaburō.
dc_description_s: Includes legend. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Relief shown by hachures. Oriented with north to the left. 1 map: col.; 46 x 35 cm,folded to 16 x 9 cm., in envelope 30 x 22 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
